lead_paragraph: Fast bowler Steven Finn will replace injured all-rounder Ben Stokes in the England team for the third test against Pakistan starting on Wednesday, test captain Alastair Cook said.

headline.print_headline: Finn to Replace Injured Stokes in Third Test
